have any say in things like that?

297
00:16:31,950 --> 00:16:33,070
But still!

298
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:36,030
It's fine, as long as
mother's  given her blessing.

299
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:38,530
That's everything  in our household.

300
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,940
Grandma, are you 
really sure about this?

301
