Of course.

302
00:16:42,130 --> 00:16:44,500
Kenji-san is excellent  groom material.

303
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:46,940
My eyes are sharp as ever.

304
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:50,000
A Jinnouchi man has to 
be solid and trustworthy!

305
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,830
